OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften cloudy and mostly dry,
OL,6,Falthough some drizzly outbreaks are
OL,7,Fpossible, mostly on western hills.
OL,8,FSome brighter spells, mainly for
OL,9,Feastern parts. Breezy, with strong
OL,10,Fgusts over high ground.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe cloud will break up
OL,13,Fovernight with clearing skies and
OL,14,Feasing winds but remaining gusty along
OL,15,Fthe coast. Relatively mild overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FBecoming cloudy and mild
OL,18,Fwith some brighter spells, later
OL,19,Foccasional rain will spread eastwards
OL,20,Facross the region by the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
